cel.app","cta":""},"html":"<p>A QR-based Print Management System that eliminates manual file transfers. Customers scan a QR code at a print shop, upload files, and select settings (color, layout, etc.). Shop owners receive requests instantly in a dedicated dashboard. Successfully onboarded the first real customer.</p>"}}]}}}